---
title: Creamy Chicken and Tomato Penne with Spinach and Cheese
description: This Creamy Chicken and Tomato Penne is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-chicken-and-tomato-penne-b17934cc-6cccc7cf.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/creamy-chicken-and-tomato-penne-62370969bed5cf4c455e7510-513fb333.pdf
author: Michael Steadman
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 718 kcal
  fat: 22.3 g
